products.product_title: Gildan Men's Crew T-Shirts, Multipack, Style G1100
about_product: Moisture wicking technology keeps you cool and dry
products.product_description: Gildan Cotton Crew Neck T-Shirts are anything but basic. Crafted with soft, breathable cotton and moisture wicking technology to keep you cool and comfortable no matter what's on the agenda. Perfect for layering or lounging - you can thank us later.

product_information.Best Sellers Rank: #3 in Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry (See Top 100 in Clothing, Shoes & Jewelry)    #1 in Men's T-Shirts

products.customers_say: Customers like the quality, fit, comfort, and value of the t-shirt. For example, they mention it's well made, soft, and comfortable. Some appreciate the color fading, and versatility. That said, some complain about the shrinkage. Opinions are mixed on thickness.
